help you remove the wasps and prevent them from returning.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Wasps Identification Color Size Description Color The most common wasp species are generally yellow and black in color but may also have white or red markings. Size Wasp can range from 10 mm to 40 mm long. Description The body structure of wasps is distinct, with a narrow waist and long, slender legs. Wasps have &#8230; <a title=\"Wasps\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wasps\/\" aria-label=\"More on Wasps\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6775,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"rank_math_lock_modified_date":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[37],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6353","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-pest-libraries"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6353"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6353"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6353\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/6775"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6353"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=6353"},{"ta